# Pillar1Adelic Module

Main entry point for PILAR 1: GEOMETRÍA ADÉLICA

This module provides the adelic geometric foundations for the Riemann Hypothesis proof.

## Files

- `adelic_measures.lean`: Haar measure and L² space
- `s_finite_systems.lean`: S-finite systems
- `poisson_radon.lean`: Poisson-Radon symmetry
- `D_operator.lean`: Canonical operator D(s)
